Summary: Silver Bullet like shape flying cloud level with no Sound
divs: Sighting DetailsI walked outside and looked up in the sky and Noticed this Bullet shape object flying in the clouds went in to get my camera took a picture and it disappeared. Came back inside and then went back outside and in the same spot I saw the other one but this one was way bigger and I knew I could get some pictures of it. So I ran inside got my camera and this is what I saw...
